<node CREATED="1576216631071" ID="ID_593079732" MODIFIED="1576216631071" TEXT="While the technology world is laser focused on the software-as-a-service (SaaS) or &#226;&#8364;&#339;cloud&#226;&#8364;&#65533; phenomenon a lot of companies with which we speak aren&#226;&#8364;&#8482;t as familiar (gasp!). That&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s changing however as SaaS solutions continue to offer a viable software option for many businesses to " />
