<node CREATED="1576216631071" ID="ID_1185218608" MODIFIED="1576216631071" TEXT="Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) is a cloud-computing approach to providing users with access to a program via the internet so the user can access it almost anywhere they have an Internet connection " />
