<node CREATED="1576216631071" ID="ID_1516388382" MODIFIED="1576216631071" TEXT="Software as a service (SaaS) allows users to connect to and use cloud-based apps over the Internet. Common examples are email calendaring and office tools (such as Microsoft Office 365). SaaS provides a complete software solution that you purchase on a pay-as-you-go basis from a cloud service provider. You rent the use of an app for your " />
