<node CREATED="1576216631071" ID="ID_928506854" MODIFIED="1576216631071" TEXT="Software as a service (or SaaS; pronounced /s&#195;&#166;s/) is a way of delivering centrally hosted applications over the Internet&#226;&#8364;&#8221;as a service. SaaS applications are sometimes called web-based software on-demand software or hosted software. Whatever the name SaaS applications run on a SaaS provider&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s servers." />
