<node CREATED="1576216631080" ID="ID_232447968" MODIFIED="1576216631080" TEXT="Identity as a Service (IDaaS) is an authentication infrastructure that is built hosted and managed by a third-party service provider. IDaaS can be thought of as single sign-on for the cloud. Download this free guide. A Guide to Successful Mobile App Development and Deployment ." />
