<node CREATED="1576216631080" ID="ID_596957434" MODIFIED="1576216631080" TEXT="IDaaS is an acronym for Identity-as-a-Service and it refers to identity and access management services that are offered through the cloud or SaaS (software-as-a-service) on a subscription basis.. This is in contrast to traditional identify and access management (IAM) solutions that are typically completely on-premises and delivered via bundled software and/or hardware means." />
