<node CREATED="1576216631080" ID="ID_1205023182" MODIFIED="1576216631080" TEXT="Get IAM right with IDaaS that enables digital transformation while reducing cloud risk &#226;&#8364;&#8221; from a managed service cloud solution to our One Identity Starling SaaS offerings. Contact Sales. Learn about our cloud strategy and how we&#226;&#8364;&#8482;ve built a cloud platform from which we can enable your organization&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s digital transformation." />
