<node CREATED="1576216631080" ID="ID_1161929486" MODIFIED="1576216631080" TEXT="Identity as a Service (IDaaS) is a cloud-based service that helps you provide fast and secure access to software and SaaS apps and securely manage identity data. Learn how Ping brings identity as a service (idaas) to the next level." />
