<node CREATED="1576216631081" ID="ID_435230293" MODIFIED="1576216631081" TEXT="Identity as a Service or IDaaS is cloud-based authentication built and operated by a third-party provider. IDaaS companies supply cloud-based authentication or identity management to enterprises who subscribe. The X-as-a-service model in information technology is easy to understand." />
