<node CREATED="1576216631083" ID="ID_528273746" MODIFIED="1576216631083" TEXT="HDFS is a distributed file system that handles large data sets running on commodity hardware. It is used to scale a single Apache Hadoop cluster to hundreds (and even thousands) of nodes. HDFS is one of the major components of Apache Hadoop the others being MapReduce and YARN." />
