<node CREATED="1576216631093" ID="ID_397000818" MODIFIED="1576216631093" TEXT="According to a survey 75% of virtualized servers require 7 or more I/O connections per device and are likely to require more frequent I/O reconfigurations. In virtualized data centers I/O performance problems are caused by running numerous virtual machines (VMs) on one server. In early server virtualization implementations the number of " />
