<node CREATED="1576216631096" ID="ID_74744377" MODIFIED="1576216631096" TEXT="Open Virtualization Format (OVF) is a specification that describes an open-standard secure efficient portable and extensible format for packaging and distributing software for virtual machines. The OVF standard is independent of any particular hypervisor or processor architecture. With the increasing demand for virtualization technology " />
</node>
