<node CREATED="1576216631096" ID="ID_1822771470" MODIFIED="1576216631096" TEXT="DMTF&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s Open Virtualization Format (OVF) standard provides the industry with a standard packaging format for software solutions based on virtual systems solving critical business needs for software vendors and cloud computing service providers." />
