<node CREATED="1576216631096" ID="ID_1692160657" MODIFIED="1576216631096" TEXT="An .ova file is simply a .tar archive file containing the Open Virtualization Format directory. It contains an .ovf file which has information about the Virtual Machine settings in XML format and a .vmdk file which is the Virtual Hard Disk file of the Virtual Machine. (.vmdk file is an open format used by VMware and VirtualBox)." />
</node>
