<node CREATED="1576216631096" ID="ID_1976753840" MODIFIED="1576216631096" TEXT="An Open Virtual Appliance file is stored in the Open Virtualization Format (OVF) as a TAR archive. Some of the files you might find within it include disk images (like VMDKs) an OVF descriptor XML-based text file ISOs or other resource files certificate files and an MF manifest file." />
</node>
