<node CREATED="1576216631102" ID="ID_151351011" MODIFIED="1576216631102" TEXT="The Atom Syndication Format is an XML language used for web feeds while the Atom Publishing Protocol (AtomPub or APP) is a simple HTTP-based protocol for creating and updating web resources. Web feeds allow software programs to check for updates published on a website." />
