<node CREATED="1576216631102" ID="ID_110422480" MODIFIED="1576216631102" TEXT="As a publishing protocol AtomPub provides a standard mechanism for creating and editing resources and resolving any arising conflicts. AtomPub extends the Atom format with a number of new publishing-related elements; at the same time it specifies the HTTP idioms that can be used to manipulate published content." />
