<node CREATED="1576216631107" ID="ID_647882512" MODIFIED="1576216631107" TEXT="Amazon EBS enables you to keep data persistently on a file system even after you shut down your EC2 instance. Amazon also provides local storage for EC2 instances that you can use while you run the instance but you lose the data when you shut down the instance. This means if you want to save that data you need to store it on Amazon EBS. " />
