<node CREATED="1576216631108" ID="ID_493608784" MODIFIED="1576216631108" TEXT="Prerequisites. Determine how many volumes you can attach to your instance. For more information see Instance Volume Limits. If a volume is encrypted it can only be attached to an instance that supports Amazon EBS encryption." />
