<node CREATED="1576216631109" ID="ID_379577271" MODIFIED="1576216631109" TEXT="2. Choose the instance you want to expand choose the Description tab and then choose the volume listed for Block devices. 3. Choose the EBS ID. 4. Choose the volume choose Actions and then choose Modify Volume. 5. Choose the Volume Type enter the Size and in the case of an io1 volume enter the desired Iops then choose Modify and " />
</node>
