<node CREATED="1576216631111" ID="ID_1862307320" MODIFIED="1576216631111" TEXT="How to Create New Amazon S3 Bucket . S3 Browser Freeware allows you to easily create Amazon S3 Buckets in all regions supported by Amazon S3: US East (N. Virginia Ohio) US-West (Northern California Oregon) Canada (Central) EU (Ireland London Paris Frankfurt Stockholm) Asia Pacific (Singapore Tokyo Mumbai Seoul Sydney Hong Kong " />
</node>
