<node CREATED="1576216631111" ID="ID_399776018" MODIFIED="1576216631111" TEXT="From the Amazon S3 console dashboard choose Create Bucket.. In Create a Bucket type a bucket name in Bucket Name.. The bucket name you choose must be globally unique across all existing bucket names in Amazon S3 (that is across all AWS customers)." />
