<node CREATED="1576216631111" ID="ID_1450363227" MODIFIED="1576216631111" TEXT="You save these in an Amazon Simple Storage Service (Amazon S3) bucket: You can store datasets that you use as your training data and model artifacts that are the output of a training job in a single bucket or in two separate buckets." />
