<node CREATED="1576216631111" ID="ID_315722297" MODIFIED="1576216631111" TEXT="node s3_listbuckets.js. This sample code can be found here on GitHub.. Creating an Amazon S3 Bucket. Create a Node.js module with the file name s3_createbucket.js.Make sure to configure the SDK as previously shown." />
