<node CREATED="1576216631111" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1562041801" LINK="https://aws.amazon.com/s3/" MODIFIED="1576216631111" TEXT="Amazon S3">
<node CREATED="1576216631111" ID="ID_501334998" MODIFIED="1576216631111" TEXT="Store your data in Amazon S3 and secure it from unauthorized access with encryption features and access management tools. S3 is the only object storage service that allows you to block public access to all of your objects at the bucket or the account level with S3 Block Public Access.S3 maintains compliance programs such as PCI-DSS HIPAA/HITECH FedRAMP EU Data Protection Directive and " />
</node>
