<node CREATED="1576216631111" ID="ID_1764143294" MODIFIED="1576216631111" TEXT="Subresources &#226;&#8364;&#8220; Amazon S3 uses the subresource mechanism to store object-specific additional information. Because subresources are subordinates to objects they are always associated with some other entity such as an object or a bucket." />
