<node CREATED="1576216631112" ID="ID_1994307075" MODIFIED="1576216631112" TEXT="Load Balancing. Amazon EKS supports the Network Load Balancer and the Classic Load Balancer through the Kubernetes service of type LoadBalancer.The configuration of your load balancer is controlled by annotations that are added to the manifest for your service." />
