<node CREATED="1576216631112" ID="ID_1830557038" MODIFIED="1576216631112" TEXT="Elastic Load Balancing automatically distributes your incoming application traffic across multiple targets such as EC2 instances. It monitors the health of registered targets and routes traffic only to the healthy targets. Elastic Load Balancing supports three types of load balancers: Application Load Balancers Network Load Balancers and " />
