<node CREATED="1576216631113" ID="ID_212950425" MODIFIED="1576216631113" TEXT="Load balancer is a service which uniformly distributes network traffic and workloads across multiple servers or cluster of servers. Load balancer in AWS increases the availability and fault tolerance of an application. AWS Elastic Load Balancer is the single point of contact to all the clients they can be sent to the nearest geographic instance or the instance with the lowest latency." />
</node>
