<node CREATED="1576216631113" ID="ID_757921953" MODIFIED="1576216631113" TEXT="Application Load Balancer. An Amazon Web Services (AWS) launched a new load balancer known as an Application load balancer (ALB) on August 11 2016. It is used to direct user traffic to the public AWS cloud. It identifies the incoming traffic and forwards it to the right resources." />
